{"tid":2180824,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中共禁止民眾在社交平台支持Trump，只可以支持拜登。","createTime":"2020-08-30T07:07:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-30T07:07:04.000Z","uid":6549,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"ebd3b981551ebd460a3a689ae705bf04082b48be","tid":2180824,"uid":6549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T07:07:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EdbC0CW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEdbC0CW.png&h=78bf5fce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n繼日前中共喉舌《环球时报》高調表態支持拜登競選美國總統後，有網民發現了，中共已經操控了民意，禁止民眾在社交平台支持Trump，只可以支持拜登。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/iguangcheng/status/1299709550577225728\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Figuangcheng%2Fstatus%2F1299709550577225728&d=XjGeTWWNN7bjI%2BfZ7PvsLBZZVu6JdVYNpUv5YkkCXtQ%3D&h=ad1b00bb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Figuangcheng%2Fstatus%2F1299709550577225728&h=e4c2cd89\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/iguangcheng/status/1299709550577225728</a><br />\n<br />\n以下是微博的情況：<br />\n<br />\n（「支持川普」或「支持特朗普」也不能出Post，但「支持拜登」就可以順利出Post.....）"}]}